text: Mourad Medelci (30 April 1943 â€“ 28 January 2019) was an Algerian politician. He was Minister of Foreign Affairs from 2007 to 2013.Page at Algerian government website . Medelci died on 28 January 2019 in Algiers from a cerebral hemorrhage, aged 75. ==References== Category:1943 births Category:2019 deaths Category:Deaths from cerebral hemorrhage Category:Algerian politicians
